About us

Born from a team of dedicated individuals with a passion for digital transformation, Catalyst launched in 2018. Since our early days, we have been evolving and helping people find quality, scalable and cost-effective solutions.

We are a leading provider of next-generation digital services enabling our clients from all around the globe to create and execute strategies for their digital transformation. Whether you’re a product owner, start-up, NGO, SME, or a big company, we will help you transform your customer experience.

Our team

From Possibility to Reality.

Catalyst runs on trust, transparency and continuous improvement in evolving our skills, seeking creative digital solutions for your business to shine globally. We believe in working meticulously making sure that your digital journey is wrapped by the best quality and protected by top security.

Where Technology blends with creativity.

Our team is a fusion of creatives and innovatives who have worked with us from the ground up. Catalyst’s human-first approach gives our illustrators, designers, developers, marketers the breathing space that they need to broaden their skills and ability. Together, we can turn your project into a one stop solution for your customers.
